# Inauguration of the academic year 2023-2024

URL: http://www.unesco.agh.edu.pl/aktualnosci/inauguration-of-the-academic-year-2023-2024/
Crawled: 2025-03-19 21:39:56

AGH University of Krakow, UNESCO AGH Chair: Inauguration of the academic year 2023-2024 2023.10.16, 12.30-14.30, AGH, bld. A0, aula 
Programme 

12.30-12.35, Welcome to the AGH University of Krakow. 
12.35-12.50, Welcome address: Prof. Jerzy Lis, AGH University Rector. 
12.50-13.00, Welcome address: Prof. Rafał Wisniowski, AGH Vice-Rector  for Cooperation. 
13.00-13.06, Welcome address: Mr Fuad Pashayev, UNESCO Paris, Head of  National Commissions and Fellowships Programme Unit. 
13.06-13.16, UNESCO AGH Chair at the AGH University of Krakow, Prof.  Janusz Szpytko, Director of the UNESCO AGH Chair. 
13.16-13.20, Welcome address: Mr Reginald “Godziwy” Sas Jaworski, The  Chanterelle King with Marshals: Mr Krzysztof Kosek and Mr Tomasz Cichoń  (Fowler Brotherhood in Krakow). 
13.20-13.30, UNESCO/ Poland Co-sponsored Fellowship Programme in  Engineering:  Fellows addresses. 
13.30-13.50, New space for Earth and humanities, lecture by prof.  Tadeusz Uhl, AGH University of Krakow. 
13.50-13.52, Gaudeamus igitur, song.
